ople.","year":44},{"id":"recRBO7FY2PSeOiUg","ref":"Acts.12.5","text":"Peter therefore was kept in prison: but prayer was made without ceasing of the church unto God for him.","year":44},{"id":"reclI9CAQVAJkXF6N","ref":"Acts.12.6","text":"And when Herod would have brought him forth, the same night Peter was sleeping between two soldiers, bound with two chains: and the keepers before the door kept the prison.","year":44},{"id":"recLyfxeyM0iDfd3j","ref":"Acts.12.7","text":"And, behold, the angel of the Lord came upon him, and a light shined in the prison: and he smote Peter on the side, and raised him up, saying, Arise up quickly. And his chains fell off from his hands.","year":44},{"id":"recXpeKFhExxGhLwO","ref":"Acts.12.8","text":"And the angel said unto him, Gird thyself, and bind on thy sandals. And so he did. And he saith unto him, Cast thy garment about thee, and follow me.","year":44}]}
